---
const { tabText, home = false } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <link href="/fontawesome/css/fontawesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/fontawesome/css/brands.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
  <link rel="icon" href="/icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest" />

  <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#5cebdf" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" />
  <title>{tabText}</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/global.css">
  <style is:global>

    @font-face {
      font-family: KenyanCoffeeRegular;
      src: url(/fonts/kenyan_coffee_rg.otf);
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: videotype;
      src: url(/fonts/videotype.otf);
    }

    .ccc-icon-bar {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      column-gap: 25px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .ccc-icon {
      font-size: 65px;
      color: #2d0203;
    }

    .ccc-icon:hover {
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #4d2223;
    }

    .bio-image {
      background-image: url(/images/nuke.jpg);
      background-position: center;
      background-size: contain;
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .ccc-grid-item_nametag {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      height: 30px;
      background-color: #003600;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
      line-height: 26px;
      font-family: videotype, sans-serif;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .ccc-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      column-gap: 15px;
      row-gap: 15px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .ccc-grid-item {
      box-shadow: 1px 1px 4px #222;
    }

    .ccc-grid-item_text {
      max-width: 350px;
      padding: 15px 10px 25px 10px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .ccc-h2 {
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 2px solid #003600;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #003600;
      color: #317620;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 2px #222;
      font-family: KenyanCoffeeRegular, sans-serif;
      font-size: 72px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .ccc-h2_backdrop {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #444;
      opacity: .5;
    }

    .ccc-text-content {
      padding: 10px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ccc-banner {
      height: 480px;
      width: auto;
      background-image: url(/images/ccc_logo_source_rectrangle_crop.png);
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      box-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #222;
    }

    .content-container {
      max-width: 1445px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    :root {
    
      --heading: var(--neutral-dark-900);
      --text: var(--neutral-dark-900);
      --text-muted: var(--neutral-dark-600);
      --primary: var(--blue-700);
      --primary-darker: var(--blue-800);
      --highlight: var(--teal-300);
      --button:var(--neutral-light-000);
      --lightBorder: var(--neutral-light-200);
      --light: var(--neutral-light-100);
      --white: var(--neutral-light-000);
      --card-radius: var(--border-radius-3);
      --font-primary: Pacaembu, sans-serif;
      --font-secondary: Mulish, sans-serif;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {

      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--font-secondary);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      display: block;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-primary);
    }

    a:link,
    a:visited {
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    a:hover,
    a:focus {
      text-decoration-color: var(--highlight);
    }

    main {
      background: var(--light);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem max(5vw, 50vw - 60ch / 2);
      width: 100vw;
      border-style: none;
    }

    .sr-only:not(:focus):not(:active) {
      clip: rect(0 0 0 0);
      clip-path: inset(50%);
      height: 1px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: absolute;
      white-space: nowrap;
      width: 1px;
    }

    .button,
    a.button {
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--white);
      display: inline-block;
      font-weight: 800;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      width: max-content;
      transition-duration: .2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: auto;
    }

    a.button:hover,
    a.button:focus,
    .button:hover,
    .button:focus {
      background: var(--primary-darker);
    }


    .container,
    .footer {
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
      width: min(90vw, 900px);
    }

    .container {
      /* background-image: url("/images/ccc_logo_source_rectrangle_crop.png");
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: contain;
      width: 100%;
      height: 400px; */
    }

    .heading {
      color: var(--heading);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer a:focus,
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .footer ul {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      list-style-type: none;
    }

    .footer li {
      margin: 0 1em;
    }

    .heart {
      display: inline-block;
      vertical-align: top;
      width: 1.1rem;
    }

    .heart img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    window['ccc'] = {};

    const ccc = window['ccc'];

    ccc.goto = goto;

    function goto(urlName) {
      const urls = {
        'twitter': 'https://x.com/TheCannCoffCrew',
        'instagram': 'https://www.instagram.com/cannabiscoffeecrew'
      };

      window.open(urls[urlName]);
    }
  </script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="content-container">
    <header class="ccc-banner"></header>
    <div class="ccc-icon-bar">
      <i class="ccc-icon fa-brands fa-x-twitter" onclick="ccc.goto('twitter')"></i>
      <i class="ccc-icon fa-brands fa-instagram" onclick="ccc.goto('instagram')"></i>
    </div>
    <h2 class="ccc-h2" style={{ marginTop: '30px' }}>About Us</h2>
    <div class="ccc-text-content">
      Welcome to the Cannabis Coffee Crew Podcast, where deep conversations brew over a cup of coffee and a cloud of cannabis smoke. We are a group of four passionate hosts who dive into everything from philosophical musings to conspiracy theories, always with an open mind and a dash of humor.

Our goal is simple: to spark thought, question the norm, and connect with listeners who enjoy exploring life’s deeper, and sometimes stranger, sides. Whether you’re here for a thought-provoking debate or just to relax and enjoy the ride, we’re glad to have you with us on this journey. Tune in, grab a cup (and a puff), and let’s dive into the unknown together.
    </div>
    <h2 class="ccc-h2">Meet the Crew</h2>
    <div class="ccc-grid">
      <div class="ccc-grid-item">
        <div class="bio-image">
          <div class="ccc-grid-item_nametag">TheBipolarNuke</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ccc-grid-item_text">
          What's up everyone! I am one of your hosts T.J. also known as Nuke.
          <br/><br/>
          I am originally from the South out in the country and now I am enjoying city life. I served in the U.S. Navy for 6 years as a Nuclear Machinist Mate. I have been a video editor for a news organization and have been a radio show producer for a popular radio station in the upstate of SC. Now I am a disabled vet here to make content and share my stories and life perspectives.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
